EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 171000Z TO 171800Z NOV:
   A. WITHIN 40 MILES OF 57-43.5N 009-08.6W.
   B. WITHIN 28 MILES OF 57-20.4N 008-18.4W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 171900Z NOV 15.
